result.title: Computer Science Interview Questions
result.content:
Hello all!

I'm fairly new to Codeforces, and this is my first post! I am very excited to improve my programming and problem solving skills :) I was wondering if there exists a list of Codeforces problems that are common CS interview questions? I'm not the greatest at technical interviews, so I am hoping for any problems that could help me hone my skills so I can be prepared for future interviews.

Thanks!
